text: Alexander Kudryavtsev and Denys Molchanov were the defending champions but chose not to defend their title. Purav Raja and Divij Sharan won the title after defeating Quino Muñoz and Akira Santillan 6–3, 4–6, [10–8] in the final. ==Seeds== ==Draw== ==References== * Main Draw Open Castilla y Leon - Doubles 2016
